### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3070/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Login via web (sets httpOnly cookies)
POST http://localhost:3070/api/auth/login/web
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login via mobile (returns tokens)
POST http://localhost:3070/api/auth/login/mobile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Refresh token (mobile)
POST http://localhost:3070/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:3070/api/auth/logout



### Get user by id
GET http://localhost:3070/api/users/24d49f49-96aa-408b-8f5d-ccd7aedca811


GET http://localhost:3070/api/auth/me